Name: Jimsonweed
Description: Also called Thorn Apple or Devil's Snare, this member of the nightshade family grows up to 5 feet tall with long, ovate leaves that are reddish-purple in color. VALUE1-10VALUE Gp
Types: Gas, Poison, Nebulizer
Gas: Each creature that starts its turn or enters this gas must succeed on a Charisma saving throw or be Frightened of the closest living creature. The target may repeat this saving throw at the end of each of its turns, ending the effect on a success. This gas has no effect on undead and constructs.
Poison: The target must succeed on a Charisma saving throw or be Frightened of the closest living creature. The target may repeat this saving throw at the end of each of its turns, ending the effect on a success. This poison has no effect on undead and constructs.
Nebulizer: May cause a backfire.
